     fhir:div [ fhir:v "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Generated Narrative: ValueSet diet-type</b></p><a name=\"diet-type\"> </a><a name=\"hcdiet-type\"> </a><p>This value set includes codes based on the following rules:</p><ul><li>Include codes from<a href=\"http://www.snomed.org/\"><code>http://snomed.info/sct</code></a><span title=\"Version is not explicitly stated. No matching Code System found\"> version Not Stated (use latest from terminology server)</span> where concept  is-a 182922004 (Dietary regime)</li><li>Include codes from<a href=\"http://www.snomed.org/\"><code>http://snomed.info/sct</code></a><span title=\"Version is not explicitly stated. No matching Code System found\"> version Not Stated (use latest from terminology server)</span> where concept  is-a 229912004 (Enteral feeding)</li><li>Include these codes as defined in <a href=\"http://www.snomed.org/\"><code>http://snomed.info/sct</code></a><span title=\"Version is not explicitly stated. No matching Code System found\"> version Not Stated (use latest from terminology server)</span><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://snomed.info/id/35011000087100\">35011000087100</a></td><td style=\"color: #cccccc\">Mixed milk feeding</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://snomed.info/id/1297276008\">1297276008</a></td><td style=\"color: #cccccc\">Breast milk feeding</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://snomed.info/id/40043006\">40043006</a></td><td style=\"color: #cccccc\">Bottle feeding of patient</td></tr></table></li></ul></div>"^^rdf:XMLLiteral ]
